    "Id": "chassisdef_fire_scorpion_FSCR-1",
    "Name": "Fire Scorpion",
    "Details": "As a quad design, the Fire Scorpion 1 lacks the amount of internal space that bipedal designs have, so its creators opted for two heavy guns; a LB 10-X Autocannon and an Ultra Autocannon/10. Each of these is fed by three tons of ammunition, giving the quad 'Mech enough shots to finish most Trials. To defend against unarmored infantry, the Fire Scorpion carries an Anti-Personnel Pod in each leg.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quad Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>",
